{"tid":1797763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聽日行動PO】和你SHOP 12.26 麻煩幫手推推置頂","createTime":"2019-12-25T16:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T07:20:24.000Z","uid":198990,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"6afca3439063b72f4191a64b1fba3c4f042404e9","tid":1797763,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAHiWdy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAHiWdy.png&h=4c2af08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先有一點要反省既係宣傳左10日都有人話唔知有行動<br />\n真係要再加大力度宣傳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日多謝同埋辛苦晒有企出嚟嘅大家！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有冇發現政權同班曱甴除咗濫捕嚟嚇人之外<br />\n已經無！晒！招！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月26日和你SHOP終極目標：<span style=\"color: red;\">落閘！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為避免重犯今日既錯誤<br />\n希望大家記住：一旦達成目標就立即撤離!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡量避免身穿blackbloc成為目標<br />\n但都可以帶件外套以防不時之須<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n<br />\n1.  <span style=\"color: pink;\">只要唔物理攻擊便衣，便衣就耐我地唔何</span><br />\n（記住現場有記者幫手睇住，反而亂捉鬼會害到手足）<br />\n<br />\n2.  <span style=\"color: orange;\">必須密切關注各TG Channel嘅情報！商場或鋪頭落閘後，綠色曱甴就會隨之而來</span><br />\n（今日幾大哨頻都有提及旺角、沙田一帶已被包圍，大家務必提高警覺）<br />\n<br />\n3.  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">落閘後可以去其他地區增援</span><br />\n（商場一旦落閘，之後個場就無人會再去，情報傳得比你想像中快）<br />\n<br />\n4.  <span style=\"color: teal;\">避免沉迷屌曱甴</span><br />\n（屌曱甴一時爽，但因屌曱甴而引發沖突嘅流血事件多不勝數，<br />\n所以間唔中屌吓等佢哋有火都發唔出嗰下就最爽）<br />\n<br />\n5.  <span style=\"color: violet;\">目標達成就要「散水」</span><br />\n（就算唔想去轉場，都避免留係原地太耐成為被攻擊目標，<br />\n保持流動性，和理SHOP係持之以恆嘅活動）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTG Channel : <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=125ffe9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"60d5885e4ab09a389b596b227885b50f6bd678a0","tid":1797763,"uid":198990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"雖然而家定咗呢幾個地點<br />\n但到時如果重曱甴嘅話（唔理你現場定TG見到）<br />\n記得要自己執生<br />\n全港商場都係得嗰堆<br />\n仲要講緊多人鳩嗚嘅商場喎<br />\n大家都知點做啦😚"},{"pid":"6b3b41b3cf0a121f5aa3654a870eab65014e1e09","tid":1797763,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0118f664d0a0a0af8ed6c68a580160f4538d2911","tid":1797763,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2a1175c887ef9a0490bed09c956697ee1bb11287","tid":1797763,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"記得溫書<br />\n<br />\n和你shop必須要keep住做，諗方法改善，而唔係畀人唱淡幾句就放棄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1797542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1797542</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"70093079a78f0915e952f3f1e301c04de511099f","tid":1797763,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e6c6d36e957795ae9c7218c0c1787ed5430010d","tid":1797763,"uid":15699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37162c9b494e537aaad089fd6c73620af4e82ff6","tid":1797763,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0daa1c6de718bf5489f42dee8b1d974d3cc5c9a4","tid":1797763,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:40:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29134e2d9ea5c2c389ec5e037b6c05b37d67cfbe","tid":1797763,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:41:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5d913b358bb3b0efefa8ae0b24b30be2993df3e","tid":1797763,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"自推 (1/10)"},{"pid":"1b8d2cd25f11350ae04c2d6fed786840f11ccb18","tid":1797763,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:44:07.000Z","msg":"推一個"},{"pid":"12d0cff2835077ffbc7cbc82beb3f707d483a454","tid":1797763,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"推兩個"},{"pid":"cfef5d5eedeb69b58be9e6f353d61a4ef00de0df","tid":1797763,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"推三個"},{"pid":"8ecb84339a633b4ef7252fcf34040df91e07ae51","tid":1797763,"uid":344455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />see u all"},{"pid":"e106b296fae814a7735e8c7a21dc1edb78e42003","tid":1797763,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"早啲訓聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68003d1b6049989c0c9dc2d7c117ec37527e157c","tid":1797763,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6010cfacfc1ea3c74135edb866fd23edaf5b2985","tid":1797763,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:36.000Z","msg":"有時唔係唔知有活動 而係活動太簡單以為寫曬d嘢上文宣可以一圖過<br />\n但其實普遍大多數人都淨係記得24號晚7-10<br />\n25號會以為都係好似24號晚同樣做法<br />\n<br />\n講真今日中午都迷惘唔知係咪真係行"},{"pid":"94abfbafbd0c10566713ce0f105fe19dee4af062","tid":1797763,"uid":275907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:47:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5a234515beca9d28d712894dc06999587abdeb62","tid":1797763,"uid":203933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:47:30.000Z","msg":"рцзн"},{"pid":"5863a84f3b3f3c41a0b9fba60ebf9dbaa3c127a1","tid":1797763,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家聽日見呀"},{"pid":"0ba96864e353a7af3ef82fdb7d7e13d4725dccbe","tid":1797763,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"我要買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0b80bab89fb7be08cf83bcee82061ff71b9418","tid":1797763,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aca8c1deda0b865ec15bb1491b4c922a38c42f7f","tid":1797763,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:50:15.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲個個商場熱熱鬧鬧<br />\n唔去shopping感受節日氣氛真係嘥哂<br />\n<br />\n冇咗price tag/唔知價錢可以去收錢排隊check<br />\n唔啱價錢揀到啱<br />\n睇啱可以問清楚啲Details 費事得物無所用嘛<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家唔好齋問唔買呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果啲狗入晒黎搞破壞落晒閘<br />\n就轉第二個商場行街<br />\n想行街都唔得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b8f9e6efbe998e9618ba2b443c9843c3810b6a","tid":1797763,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>SHOP商場戰略檢討與重點</ins></strong></span> 幫手share<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>1) 12點好撤，再留係度攬炒指數低</ins></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">咁夜對政權既傷害係邊度? 個撚個都返鳩哂屋企訓教, 車又少。同玩平原戰 自殺有咩分別? 大家要記住個目標係乜野。街上又無其他路人幫你地cover, 過左12點又無車走。好似琴日MK咁, D人又話走唔撚到比狗包圍住。咁唔該你地今日咪撚再要呀寶出動</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>2) 落閘就目標已達成, 可以轉場</strong></ins></span><br />\n商場落閘基本上都係因為D狗入撚哂黎, 咁達成目標 無需要再屌狗同戀戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>3) 回馬槍，D狗走個時唔撚好再上前</ins></strong></span><br />\n尤其是商場入面，例如琴日ＹＯＨＯ已經比人回馬槍左起碼3-4次。每次都捉撚左2-3個。屌狗還屌狗, 你地係後面屌就爽, 企前面既街坊就中伏。唔好再做豬隊友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>4) 街坊被捕個時麻煩街坊咪撚係度嘈</ins></strong></span><br />\n琴日已經有幾次係因為街坊太嘈, 個街坊大聲叫都無人聽到佢講乜, 咁樣同害9自己友無分別。一陣無名無姓無資料, 係咪想人地被消失??"},{"pid":"b5dc35bfcf9da4fde11e3ee891d4016b940d58c1","tid":1797763,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=df7be0f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"d0ea7341a725618b077203a3b011d28b94e75837","tid":1797763,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"其實便衣係會主動拉人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc683513c6932a7e4eafe4fae68442df6405d3a","tid":1797763,"uid":254028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"Tui 行動PO"},{"pid":"0d20eccd137196e4c8227bc2230d19806637dcb4","tid":1797763,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"目標:<br />\n排到收銀大大條龍<br />\n貨場員工一齊解決顧客疑問<br />\n突然香港服務業好客之道振興香港經濟<br />\n<br />\